    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <opener><salute>Dear Sir</salute></opener>
                <p>Many thanks for y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> favor &amp;c. as to <bibl><title ref="bi0103">the abercrombie</title></bibl>, <persName ref="pe0309"><unclear reason="illegible">yr</unclear> master of the ship</persName>
                    will not deliver it. I am amazed that <persName ref="pe0156">M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Lows</persName> draft has not reached me. pray
                    inform him of it by return of post, for if it does not come while I am here, I
                    must find some other way of sending the promised aid. This is a point of honor.
                    I would by no means fail in. If His draft does not come I will send him one,
                    which I wish had been done at first.</p>
                <p>Be so good to <bibl><title ref="bi0115">M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Ridpathâ€™s
                                <unclear reason="illegible">London</unclear> history</title></bibl>.
                    I can find no bookseller here that knows of it. He only wants names.</p>
                <closer><salute>I am Dear Sir your faithfull H.S.</salute>
                    <signed><persName ref="pe0232">T Pennant.</persName></signed>
                <dateline><placeName ref="pl0699">London</placeName> April 7<hi rend="superscript">th</hi>. 1774.</dateline></closer>

                <postscript>
                    <p>I stay here a little more than a fortnight.</p>
                    <p>I have got a <bibl><title ref="bi0739">Regiam majestatem</title></bibl>. Y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Letter with the prints is just come. Y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> printers take off Prints most wretchedly.</p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
            <div>
                <p><address>
                        <addrLine>M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>Paton</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>Custom House</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>Edenburgh</addrLine>
                    </address></p>
                <p>Free<gap reason="illegible" unit="words" quantity="1"/></p>
                <p><stamp>FREE</stamp></p>
                <p><stamp>7/AP</stamp></p>
            </div>
        </body>
